s is half a gig lower than the average converted file.","The quality of the converted movie file made by this program is a mixed bag. We noticed significant image flaws in the converted video when compared to a digital download of the same movie. Pixilation, scaling blur and ripple banding were all present, and while some users may not notice or care about these flaws, those who enjoy a high-quality video experience will be disappointed at the end result.","Conversely, the converted audio produced by this program is perfect. It retained all the subtle details that audiophiles will appreciate. This aspect can be especially useful if you choose to extract only the audio portions of a DVD."]},"id":"c58eb596-89a4-4711-a3d4-782e4e22e7e1","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"acc2139f-928e-45b9-b1da-7745fc29b12c","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["MacX DVD Ripper is an adequate application for converting your DVDs for playback on your iPad. It is quite easy to use and has conversion profiles for nearly every model of Apple’s tablet. The only major downside of the program is that the quality of the converted video may disappoint users who value a high-quality, detailed picture."]},"id":"933ea12b-d13e-41b6-9e03-38fb917cd1ab","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_66473","url":"/macx-dvd-ripper-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"danny-chadwick","url":"/author/danny-chadwick","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"Danny Chadwick","dateModified":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","id":"DhF8Hg8QQde8MtLyq8X8JN","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2015-08-07T14:39:25Z","datePublished":"2015-08-07T14:39:25Z","name":"MacX DVD Ripper Pro","synopsis":"Like its name suggests, MacX DVD Ripper Pro is a DVD converter designed specifically for Mac users. It lets you convert your DVDs into a digital format that you can import into iTunes and then sync to and watch on your iPad.","review":{